### SCSS
- MUST use SCSS spacing variables for paddings, margins, gaps, etc
- Example: spacing/page-margins -> $spacing-page-margins

- MUST use matching CSS variables for colors
- MUST not include "elements" in color variables
- Example: elements/general/bg -> var(--general-bg)

- MUST use typogra mixins from _font-styles.scss
- Do not include "normal" in typogra mixins
- Example: body/normal -> @include body;
- Example: body/small -> @include body-small
- Use (false) if you want a custom margin bottom
- Example: @include body-small(false)

- MUST use mobile first
- MUST use media-breakpoint-up mixin for media queries
- MUST use `@use "helpers/init" as *` to load assets.

- If padding/margin/borders should be applied to the top and bottom use `{padding|margin|border}-block: {value}`
- If padding/margin/borders should be applied to the left and right use `{padding|margin|border}-inline: {value}`